name: Dayforce
description: Dayforce Inc., together with its subsidiaries, operates as a human capital management (HCM) software company in the United States, Canada, Australia, and internationally. The company offers Dayforce, a cloud HCM platform that provides human resources, payroll and tax, workforce management, wallet, benefits, and talent intelligence functionalities; and Powerpay, a cloud HR and payroll solution for the small business market. It also provides payroll and payroll-related services; and professional services for its solutions, which include training and implementation consulting services.
